  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he said, you go to the cookhouse lunch time, whenever there's meals, and you tell them I sent you, and they should give you a vegetarian meal.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I used to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You see. ?] And they would offer you these facilities?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You was allowed to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A notice always come through from the War Office, all Jewish personnel who wish to observe the festival of Passover or the Jewish New Year, they'd get a circular from the war office from the senior Jewish chaplain, and they knew fully well been a formal Jewish regiment there, that you applied for it subject-- the army has got funny ways of talking, that they throw in French words.",
      "word_count": 69
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Instead of like, subject's conditions that prevail, it will say, subject to the exigencies of the services permitting, he should be allowed to go home in lieu of and not in addition to normal leave.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you were in some way penalized, but at least you had the opportunity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, so, I used to go home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was fortunate I was able to go home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, from Hounslow, that was like [? week's ?] training, you went over to Hounslow Heath.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was before Heathrow was ever thought of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Heathrow didn't exist at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was Hounslow Heath.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there you was at what they called advanced training, and from there you went to battalion, and then from there you went to whatever you--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You went on a rifle range in [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Perp, ?] right?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to show you how to use a rifle or machine guns or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they use to have target, like, you had to pass out [? that ?] you got shot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, what happened, the old soldiers knew the trick, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
